uence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be on the Prophet of Allah, Peace be on the Messenger of Allah, Peace be on Muhammad the leader of the Messengers, Peace be on Muhammad the leader of the foremost ones. Peace be on one whom Allah sent as a mercy to the universe. Peace be on you, O Prophet and the mercy and blessings of Allah be upon you.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Salaam ho Allah ke Nabi par. Salaam ho Allah ke Rasool par. Salaam ho Rasoolo’n ke sardaar Hazrat Muhammad (s.a.w.a) par. Salaam ho awwaleen ke sardaar Hazrat Muhammad (s.a.w.a) par. Salaam ho aakhareen ke sardaar Hazrat Muhammad (s.a.w.a) par. Salaam ho un janaab par jin ko Allah ne rehmatulil aalameen bana kar bheja. Salaam ho ay nabi aur rehmat ho Allah ki aur uski barkate’n.", "Urdu": "سلام ہو اللہ کے نبیؐ پر، سلام ہو اللہ کے رسولؐ پر، سلام ہو رسولوں کے سردار حضرت محمدؐ پر،سلام ہو اولین کے سردار حضرت محمدؐ پر، سلام ہو آخرین کے سردار حضرت محمدؐ پر، سلام ہو ان جناب پر جن کو اللہ نے رحمت للعالمین بنا کر بھیجا سلام ہو اے نبیؐ اور رحمت ہو اللہ کی اور اس کی برکتیں۔", "RArabic": "ASSALAAMO A’LAA NABIYYIL LAAHE ASSALAAMO A’LAA RASOOLIL LAAHE ASSALAAMO A’LAA MOHAMMADIN SAYYEDIL MURSALEENA ASSALAAMO A’LA MOHAMMADIN SAYYEDIL AWWALEENA ASSALAAMO A’LAA MOHAMMADIN SAYYEDIL AAKHEREENA ASSALAAMO A’LAA MAN BA-A’SAHUL LAAHO RAHMATAN LIL-A’ALAMEENA ASSALAAMO A’LAYKA AYYOHAN NABIYYO WA RAHMATUL LAAHE WA BARAKAATOHU.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی نَبِیِّ اللہِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی رَسُوْلِ اللہِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ سَیِّدِ الْمُرْسَلِیْنَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ سَیِّدِ الْاَوَّلِیْنَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ سَیِّدِ الْاٰخِرِیْنَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی مَنْ بَعَثَہُ اللہُ رَحْمَۃً لِّلْعَالَمِیْنَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكَ اَیُّھَا النَّبِیُّ وَرَحْمَۃُ اللہِ وَبَرَكَاتُہٗ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013032, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be on Fatima, the daughter of Asad, the Hashimite, Peace be upon you O truthful and contented one; Peace be upon you O virtuous and pure one. Peace be upon you O virtuous and pure one; Peace be upon You O noble and contented one. Peace be upon you O one who looked after Muhammad, the seal of the Prophets. Peace be upon you O mother of the leader of the successors.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Salaam ho Bibi Fatema binte Asad par jo Hashmiya hai. Aap par salaam ho ay siddiqa aur Khuda ki pasandida. Salaam ho aap par keh aap parhez-gaar o paakeeza, Aap par Salaam ho ay izzat o raza ki maalika. Aap par Salaam ho ay khaateem Muhammad (s.a.w.a) ki sar-parast. Aap par Salaam ho ay ausiya ke sardaar ki waalidah. Aap par Salaam ho ay woh jis ne Allah ke Rasool aur nabiyyo’n ke khaateem par shafqat wa maher-baani ki.", "Urdu": "سلام ہو بی بی فاطمہ بنت اسد پر جو ہاشمیہ ہیں آپ پر سلام ہو اے صدیقہ اور خدا کی پسندیدہ سلام ہو آپ پر آپ پرہیز گار و پاکیزہ آپ پر سلام ہوآپ عزّت و رضا کی مالکہ ہیں آپ پر سلام ہوکہ آپ خاتم محمدؐ کی سرپرست ہیں آپ پر سلام ہو اوصیاء کے سردار کی والدہ آپ پرسلام ہو اے وہ جس نے اللہ کے رسولؐ اور نبیوں کے خاتم پر شفقت و مہربانی کی۔", "RArabic": "ASSALAAMO A’LAA FAATEMATA BINTE ASADENIL HAASHEMIYYATE ASSALAAMO A’LAYKE AYYATOHS SIDDEEQATUL MARZIYYATO ASSALAAMO A’LAYKE AYYATOHAT TAQIYYATUN NAQIYYATO ASSALAAMO A’LAYKE AYYATOHAL KAREEMATUR RAZIYYATO ASSALAAMO A’LAYKE YAA KAAFELATA MOHAMMADIN KHAATAMIN NABIYYEENA ASSALAAMO A’LAYKA YAA WAALEDATA SAYYEDIL WASIYYEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلٰی فَاطِمَۃَ بِنْتِ اَسَدٍ الْھَاشِمِیَّۃِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكِ اَیَّتُھَا الصِّدِّیْقَۃُ الْمَرْضِیَّۃُ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكِ اَیَّتُھَا التَّقِیَّۃُ النَّقِیَّۃُ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكِ اَیَّتُھَا الْكَرِیْمَۃُ الرَّضِیَّۃُ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكِ یَا كَافِلَۃَ مُحَمَّدٍ خَاتَمِ النَّبِیِّیْنَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكِ یَا وَالِدَۃَ سَیِّدِ الْوَصِیِّیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013033, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Peace be upon you who showed compassion to the Prophet of Allah, seal of the Prophets; Peace be upon you O one who raised the trustworthy friend of Allah; Peace be upon you, on your soul and on your pure body; May peace, mercy and blessings be upon you and on your son.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Aap par Salaam ho ay woh jis ne Allah ke imaan-daar Wali ki parwarish ki. Salaam ho aap par, aap ki rooh par aur aap ke paakeeza badan par. Aap par Salaam ho aur aap ki aulaad par Khuda ki rehmat aur uski barkate’n ho.", "Urdu": "آپ پر سلام ہو اے وہ جس نے اللہ کے امانت دار ولی کی پرورش کی سلام ہو آپ پر آپ کی روح پر اور آپ کے پاکیزہ بدن پر آپ پرسلام ہو اور آپ کی اولاد پر خدا کی رحمت اور اس کی برکتیں ہوں۔", "RArabic": "ASSALAAMO A’LAYKA YAA MAN ZAHARAT SHA-FA-QATOHAA A’LAA RASOOLIL LAAHE KHATAMIN NABIYYEENA ASSALAAMO A’LAYKA YAA MAN TARBEYATOHAA LE-WALIYYIL LAAHIL AMEENE ASSALAAMO A’LAYKE WA A’LAA ROOHEKE WA BADANEKIT TA, ASSALAAMO A’LAYKE WA ALAA WALADEKA WA RAHMATULLAHE WA BARAKAATOHU.", "ArabicText1": "اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكِ یَا مَنْ ظَھَرَتْ شَفَقَتُھَا عَلٰی رَسُوْلِ اللہِ خَاتَمِ النَّبِیّیْنَ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكِ یَا مَنْ تَرْبِیَتُھَا لِوَلِیِّ اللہِ الْاَمِیْنِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكِ وَعَلٰی رُوْحِكِ وَبَدَنِكِ الطَّاھِرِ۔ اَلسَّلَامُ عَلَیْكِ وَعَلٰی وَلَدِكَ وَرَحْمَۃُ اللہِ وَبَرَكَاتُہٗ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013034, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "I bear witness that you supported in the best manner possible and fulfilled your obligation and strived for the pleasure of Allah and exerted yourself in protecting the Prophet of Allah, being aware of his status; believing in his truthfulness; acknowledging his prophecy, perceiving his blessings; taking responsibility of his upbringing, dealing with him affectionately; ready to serve him; choosing what please him, preferring what he like.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Mai gawahi deta hu keh aap ne Hazrat Rasool (s.a.w.a) ki achchhi sar-parasti (parwarish) ki, us amaanat ko sanbhaala aur Khuda ki raza mein kosha’n (koshish karti) rahi. Aap Khuda ke Rasool ki hifaazat karne mein kaamyaab rahi jab keh aap unke haq se waaqif, unki sachchaayi par imaan rakhne waali, unki nabuwat ka eteraaf karne waali, unko mili huwi neymat ko pehchaan ne waali, unki parwarish ki zimme-daar, unki zaat par maher-baan, unki khidmat ke liye har waqt haazir aur unki khushi chaahti rahi.", "Urdu": "میں گواہی دیتا ہوں کہ آپ نے حضرت رسول ؐکی اچھی سرپرستی کی اس امانت کو سنبھالا اور خدا کی رضا میں کوشاں رہیں آپ خدا کے رسولؐ کی حفاظت کرنے میں کامیاب رہیں جب کہ آپ ان کے حق سے واقف ان کی سچائی پر ایمان رکھنے والی ان کی نبوت کا اعتراف کرنے والی ان کو ملی ہوئی نعمت کو پہچاننے والی ان کی پرورش کی ذمہ داران کی ذات پر مہربان ان کی خدمت کے لئے ہمہ وقت حاضر اور ان کی خوشی چاہتی رہیں۔", "RArabic": "ASH-HADO ANNA-KE AHSAN-TIL KEFAA-LATA WA ADDAIY-TIL AMAA-NATA WAJTA-HADTE FEE MARZAA-TIL LAAHE WA BAALAGH-TE FEE HIFZE RASOOLIL LAAHE AA’RE-FATAN BE-HAQQE-HI MO-MENATAN BE-SIDQE-HI MO’TARE-FATAN BE-NABUWWATE-HI MUSTAB-SERA-TAN BE-NE’MATE-HI KAAFE-LATAN BE-TARBE-YATEHI MUSHFE-QATAN A’LAA NAFSE-HI WAAQE-FATAN A’LAA KHIDMATE-HI MUKHTAA-RATAN REZAA-HO.", "ArabicText1": "اَشْھَدُ اَنَّكِ اَحْسَنْتِ الْكِفَالَۃَ وَاَدَّیْتِ الْاَمَانَۃَ وَاجْتَھَدْتِ فِیْ مَرْضَاتِ اللہِ وَبَالَغْتِ فِیْ حِفْظِ رَسُوْلِ اللہِ عَارِفَۃً بِحَقِّہٖ مُؤْمِنَۃً بِصِدْقِہٖ مُعْتَرِفَۃً بِنُبُوَّتِہٖ مُسْتَبْصِرَۃً بِنِعْمَتِہٖ كَافِلَۃً بِتَرْبِیَتِہٖ مُشْفِقَۃً عَلٰی نَفْسِہٖ وَاقِفَۃً عَلٰی خِدْمَتِہٖ مُخْتَارَۃً رِضَاہُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013035, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "I bear witness that you spent your life on the (true) faith and adhering to the most noble religion, being pleased and contented, pure, clean, guarded and virtuous. May Allah be pleased and satisfied with you; may He make heaven as your house and permanent abode.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Mai gawahi deta hu keh aap duniya se gayi to imaan ke saath aur behtareen deen se waabasta rakhte huwe jab keh aap Khuda se raazi aur Woh aap se raazi, aap paakeeza, nek, parhez-gaar, paak-baaz thi. Pas Khuda aap se raazi huwa, Us ne aap ko khush kiya aur Us ne aap ko Jannat mein maqaam o manzil ataa kiya.", "Urdu": "میں گواہی دیتا ہوں کہ آپ دنیا سے گئیں تو ایمان کے ساتھ اور بہترین دین سے وابستگی رکھتے ہوئے جب کہ آپ خدا سے راضی وہ آپ سے راضی آپ پاکیزہ نیک پرہیزگار پاک باز تھیں پس خدا آپ سے راضی ہوا اس نے آپ کو خوش کیا اور اس نے آپ کو جنت میں مقام و منزل عطا کی۔", "RArabic": "WA ASH-HADO ANNA-KE MAZEE-TE A’LAL IMAANE WAT-TAMASSO-KE BE-ASHRA-FIL AD-YAANE RAAZE-YATAN MARZIY-YATAN TAAHE-RATAN ZAKIY-YATAN TAQIY-YATAN NAQIY-YATAN FARAZE-YAL LAAHO A’N-KE WA ARZAA-KE WA JA-A’LAL JANNATA MANZELE-KE WA MAAWAA-KE.", "ArabicText1": "وَاَشْھَدُ اَنَّكِ مَضَیْتِ عَلَی الْاِیْمَانِ وَالتَّمَسُّكِ بِاَشْرَفِ الْاَدْیَانِ رَاضِیَۃً مَرْضِیَّۃً طَاھِرَۃً زَكِیَّۃً تَقِیَّۃً نَقِیَّۃً فَرَضِیَ اللہُ عَنْكِ وَاَرْضَاكِ وَجَعَلَ الْجَنَّۃَ مَنْزِلِكِ وَمَاْوٰیكِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013036, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, send your greetings on Muhammad and the family of Muhammad and make my visiting her beneficial to me and make me firm in my love for her and do not deprive me of her intercession and the intercession of the Imams from her loins; so grant me her company and gather me with her and with her pure children.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Muhammad (s.a.w.a) wa Aale Muhammad (a.s) par rehmat farma aur mujhe us Bibi ki ziyarat se nafa ataa kar, mujhe unki mohabbat par qaaem rakh aur mujh ko unki shafa’at aur unki aulaad mein se Aimma (a.s) ki shafa’at se mehroom na farma, mujhe us Bibi ki ham-saayegi naseeb kar aur mujhe us Bibi ke saath aur uski paakeeza aulaad ke saath mehshoor farma.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! محمدؐ و آل محمدؐپر رحمت فرما اور مجھے اس بی بی کی زیارت سے نفع عطا کر مجھے اس کی محبت پر قائم رکھ اور مجھ کو اس کی شفاعت اور اس کی اولاد میں سے ائمہؑ کی شفاعت سے محروم نہ فرما مجھے اس بی بی کی ہمسائیگی نصیب کر اور مجھے اس بی بی کے ساتھ اور اس کی پاکیزہ اولاد کے ساتھ محشور فرما۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA SALLE A’LAA MOHAMMADIW WA AALE MOHAMMADIN WAN FA’NEE BE-ZIYAARATE-HA WA SABBIT-NEE A’LAA MOHABBATE-HAA WA LAA TAHRIM-NEE SHAFAA-A’TA-HAA WA SHAFAA-A’TAL AIMMATE MIN ZURRIY-YATE-HAA WAR-ZUQNI MURAA-FAQATA-HAA WAH-SHURNEE MA-A’HAA WA MA-A’ AWLAADE-HAT TAAHE-REENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰھُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰی مُحَمَّدٍ وَاٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَانْفَعْنِیْ بِزِیَارَتِھَا وَثَبِّتْنِیْ عَلٰی مَحَبَّتِھَا وَلَا تَحْرِمْنِیْ شَفَاعَتَھَا وَشَفَاعَۃَ الْاَئِمَّۃِ مِنْ ذُرِّیَّتِھَا وَارْزُقْنِیْ مُرَافَقَتَھَا وَاحْشُرْنِیْ مَعَھَا وَمَعَ اَوْلَادِھَا الطَّاھِرِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1013037, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah, do not make it my last visit to her and grant me another visit to her as long as You keep me alive and if You cause me to die then gather me with her ranks and include me amongst those receiving her intercession by Your mercy, O Most Merciful of the Merciful ones.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Mai ne Fatema binte Asad (a.s) ki jo ziyarat ki hai usey mera aakhri mauqa qaraar na de aur mujhe baar baar yahan aana naseeb farma jab tak Tu mujhe zindah rakkhe aur jab mujhe maut de to mujhe is Bibi ke giroh mein utha aur mujhe uski shafa’at mein daakhil farma ba-waasta apni rehmat ke, ay sab se ziyadah rahem waale.", "Urdu": "اے معبود! میں نے فاطمہ بنت اسد کی جو زیارت کی ہے اسے میرا آخری موقع قرار نہ دے اور مجھے بار بار یہاں آنا نصیب فرما جب تک تو مجھے زندہ رکھے اور جب مجھے موت دے تو مجھے اس بی بی کے گروہ میں اٹھا اور مجھے اس کی شفاعت میں داخل فرما اپنی رحمت کے واسطے سےاے سب سے زیادہ رحم والے۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA LAA TAJ-A’L-HO AAKHE-RAL A’HDE MIN ZIYAA-RATEE AIYYAA-HAA WAR-ZUQNIL A’W-DA ILAI-HAA ABA-DAN MAA AB-QAITA-NEE WA IZAA TAWAF-FAITA-NEE FAHSHUR-NEE FEE ZUMRATE-HAA WA ADKHIL-NEE FEE SHAFAA A’TEHAA BE-RAHMATE-KA YAA AR-HAMAR RAAHE-MEENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰھُمَّ لَا تَجْعَلْہُ اٰخِرَ الْعَھْدِ مِنْ زِیَارَتِیْ اِیَّاھَا وَارْزُقْنِیْ الْعَوْدَ اِلَیْھَا اَبَدًا مَا اَبْقَیْتَنِیْ وَاِذَا تَوَفَّیْتَنِیْ فَاحْشُرْنِیْ فِیْ زُمْرَتِھَا وَاَدْخِلْنِیْ فِیْ شَفَاعَتِھَا بِرَحْمَتِكَ یَا اَرْحَمَ الرَّاحِمِیْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "